---
title: Cheesy Chicken Parmigiana with Double Bacon Wedges & Apple Salad
description: A chicken parmigiana is a fan favourite that everyone will be excited about. How about adding a little twist to really get those cheers of excitement going, like making them into chicken tenders with a side of bacon wedges? Three cheers for the chicken parmigiana!
